Sentencas: Solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) are devices that offer high efficiency power output with negligible emissions.
Titulo: Gelcasting of Strontium Doped Lanthanum Manganite for Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Applications

Sentencas: Cathode supported tubular SOFCs consist of porous cathode tubes made up of strontium doped lanthanum manganite, La1-xSrxMnO3 (LSM) that work as functional component as well as structural support for the rest of the cell components.
Titulo: Gelcasting of Strontium Doped Lanthanum Manganite for Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Applications

Sentencas: Gelcasting is one of the most suitable methods for the fabrication of porous ceramics.
Titulo: Gelcasting of Strontium Doped Lanthanum Manganite for Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Applications

Sentencas: This paper describes the fabrication of porous LSM cathode by gelcasting process.
Titulo: Gelcasting of Strontium Doped Lanthanum Manganite for Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Applications

Sentencas: Gelcasting parameters such as monomer concentration, powder volume fraction, pH of the slurry, etc were optimized.
Titulo: Gelcasting of Strontium Doped Lanthanum Manganite for Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Applications

Sentencas: Slow drying of green specimens minimized warpage and cracking.
Titulo: Gelcasting of Strontium Doped Lanthanum Manganite for Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Applications

Sentencas: Sintered specimens with controlled porosity were obtained by the use of suitable pore-forming agents.

Sentencas: The coefficient of thermal expansion (CTE) of sintered specimens was measured, which was found matching with the CTE values of cell components reported in the literature.

Sentencas: These results have shown the suitability of the gelcast generated LSM cathodes for SOFC applications.
